{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x1748d2",
      "back_en": "Are you all ready?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1748f2",
      "back_en": "Haku, this area looks safe.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'clear' como 'segura' é adequado no contexto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174943",
      "back_en": "before they realize what's going on.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174998",
      "back_en": "straight to my target like this.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'target location' reduzido a 'alvo', mas mantém sentido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1749ef",
      "back_en": "during the dead of night, while they sleep.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Tempo verbal: 'slept' (passado) vs 'dormem' (presente)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174c63",
      "back_en": "bad-mouthing me over there?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174cb2",
      "back_en": "you drew Oshtor's attention, with such artifice.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Adequado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174d3c",
      "back_en": "scary.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174d75",
      "back_en": "the only thing he's good at.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'negócio' coloquial mas ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174d96",
      "back_en": "Is this really how these guys see me...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel; 'rapazes' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174dbf",
      "back_en": "Um... Sir Haku, I... I think you're amazing!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174dec",
      "back_en": "Uh... th-thanks.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174dfd",
      "back_en": "Anyway, let's finish this quick.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174e5a",
      "back_en": "I don't think that's anything praiseworthy.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174e8d",
      "back_en": "To think he would dare hide behind my name!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174eee",
      "back_en": "I never imagined he could sink that low.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174f17",
      "back_en": "Mm? Oh, yes. Right.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174f2c",
      "back_en": "Get a grip... Have to stick to the story.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'Controla-te'/'Tem de' são pt-PT; pt-BR usaria 'Se controla'/'Tenho de'. 'colar com a história' soa estranho."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174f8b",
      "back_en": "somewhere we wouldn't be seen.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x174fc6",
      "back_en": "...What do you want?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17500b",
      "back_en": "wanted criminal? Or have you come to capture me?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17506f",
      "back_en": "heavy on her...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Aceitável fora de contexto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1750df",
      "back_en": "know.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x175165",
      "back_en": "are?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1751aa",
      "back_en": "you. How can you actually not know...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1751ff",
      "back_en": "I can't remember every detail.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Nuance de 'be expected to' perdida mas aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1752b7",
      "back_en": "of most of the crimes you're accused of?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Falta 'de' antes de 'que', mas compreensível."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1752e1",
      "back_en": "What do you mean by that?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17537c",
      "back_en": "crime?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1753e7",
      "back_en": "he was the one who framed you in the beginning.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'in the first place' como 'no começo' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1757e0",
      "back_en": "that's what will convince her...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x175bc7",
      "back_en": "the princess. She still seemed to be feeling guilty.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x175e38",
      "back_en": "Yes! An admirable creed to live by.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x17686e",
      "back_en": "the right thing... Is justice really on our side?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel; 'justica' sem cedilha é typo menor."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x1771f2",
      "back_en": "Denebokshiri, it ceases to be a lie.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x177323",
      "back_en": "*Cough, hack* D-Dammit, what's going on!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Tom e sentido preservados."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 36
}